---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cancellation & Refund Policy - Sri Janaki Mahal Trust">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#faf8f3] py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cancellation & Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 space-y-8">
        
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Policy Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            This Cancellation and Refund Policy outlines the terms and conditions for canceling bookings and requesting refunds 
            at Sri Janaki Mahal Trust. We understand that plans may change, and we strive to accommodate our guests while 
            maintaining fair policies for all parties.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            All cancellation requests must be made through our official channels: WhatsApp (+91 7250364323), phone, or email (vedpragyabharat@gmail.com).
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Standard Cancellation Policy -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Standard Cancellation Policy</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-700">
              All cancellation requests must be made at least 24 hours before your scheduled check-in time to be eligible for any refund.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="min-w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                <tr>
                  <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Cancellation Time</th>
                  <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Refund Amount</th>
                  <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Processing Time</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">More than 48 hours before check-in</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-green-600 font-semibold">100% refund</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">3-5 business days</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">24-48 hours before check-in</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-yellow-600 font-semibold">50% refund</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">3-5 business days</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">Less than 24 hours before check-in</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-red-600 font-semibold">No refund</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">N/A</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">No-show (no cancellation)</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-red-600 font-semibold">No refund</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">N/A</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Special Circumstances -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Special Circumstances</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">3.1 Emergency Cancellations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We understand that emergencies can occur. The following circumstances may qualify for special consideration:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Medical emergencies (with documentation)</li>
            <li>Death in the family</li>
            <li>Natural disasters affecting travel</li>
            <li>Government-imposed travel restrictions</li>
            <li>Flight cancellations beyond your control</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Emergency cancellations will be reviewed on a case-by-case basis and may qualify for full or partial refunds 
            regardless of timing, subject to verification.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">3.2 Weather-Related Cancellations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            In case of severe weather conditions that make travel unsafe or impossible, we will work with you to reschedule 
            your stay or provide appropriate refunds.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Refund Process -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Refund Process</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">4.1 How to Request a Refund</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Contact us immediately via WhatsApp (+91 7250364323) or email (vedpragyabharat@gmail.com)</li>
            <li>Provide your booking details (name, phone number, check-in date)</li>
            <li>Explain the reason for cancellation</li>
            <li>Submit any required documentation (for emergency cases)</li>
            <li>Wait for confirmation of your refund request</li>
          </ol>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">4.2 Refund Processing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Once your refund is approved:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Refunds will be processed within 3-5 business days</li>
            <li>Refunds will be issued to the original payment method</li>
            <li>You will receive a confirmation email once processed</li>
            <li>Bank processing times may vary (additional 2-7 days)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Non-Refundable Items -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The following items are non-refundable under any circumstances:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Services already consumed (meals, amenities used)</li>
            <li>Third-party charges (if applicable)</li>
            <li>Processing fees (if any)</li>
            <li>Damages to property or facilities</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Modification Policy -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Booking Modifications</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Instead of canceling, you may be able to modify your booking:
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">6.1 Date Changes</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Date changes are subject to availability and may incur additional charges if rates have increased.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">6.2 Room Type Changes</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Room upgrades or downgrades are subject to availability and rate differences.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Dispute Resolution -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Dispute Resolution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you disagree with our refund decision:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Contact our management team via email with detailed explanation</li>
            <li>Provide supporting documentation</li>
            <li>Allow 5-7 business days for review</li>
            <li>We will provide a written response with our final decision</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <!-- Force Majeure -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Force Majeure</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Sri Janaki Mahal Trust shall not be liable for any failure to perform its obligations due to circumstances 
            beyond our reasonable control, including but not limited to acts of God, natural disasters, war, terrorism, 
            government actions, or other unforeseeable events.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            For cancellation requests, refund inquiries, or questions about this policy, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Sri Janaki Mahal Trust</strong></p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Vasudev Gath, Karsewakpuram</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Ayodhya, Uttar Pradesh 224123</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">India</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Phone: <a href="tel:+917250364323" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700">+91 7250364323</a></p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/917250364323" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700">+91 7250364323</a></p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Email: <a href="mailto:vedpragyabharat@gmail.com" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700">vedpragyabharat@gmail.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Policy Updates -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify this Cancellation and Refund Policy at any time. Changes will be effective 
            immediately upon posting on our website. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance 
            of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
